metadata.name: freaking me out #1/3
metadata.description:
"freaking me out" is a song about my post-Mormon sexual awakening. It Juxtaposes an irresistible dance groove with ambiguous and never-settling chord changes. I wanted to create an experience that feels so good, and so wrong. Melodies that stick around in your head longer than you might want with occasionally uncomfortable lyrics.

The Royalties of this NFT will be distributed to the visual artist, and all the musicians involved in its creation.  
3% to visual artist  and a 3-way even split of 15.66% to the Writers and Producers of this record, totaling 49.99%.

Collectors will take 50.01% of resale royalties.
